Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:31.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(540,0)}下集  「魔法之书」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.46,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:43.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:48.68,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:54.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.94,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:09.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:14.45,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.75,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.63,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:32.39,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:38.89,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:46.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.46,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}记下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:43.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它变成现实的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:48.68,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折叠起来的书页  正在呼唤着我去翻阅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:54.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}扬起的风沙尘土  可能会让你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要担心  我们在坚定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是开端有点意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你记录下的寂寞经历
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.94,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}无法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:09.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我会解读成未来的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:14.45,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能让我感到世界焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.75,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我来吧  就这样出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.63,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}没有什么好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:26.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飞梦想  相约明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:32.39,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}书写这篇历险记的时候  即使呼唤你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:38.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味着迷路  而是共同启程的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:46.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}没错…你与我 不会停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:53.73,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:22:01.53,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.27,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.01,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:28.20,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.48,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.81,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:46.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:54.36,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:53.73,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之铃  上锁之声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:22:01.53,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它们的流淌中  我们逐渐成长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.27,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑欢笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:11.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}终归会远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.01,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:28.20,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要将它流传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.48,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:37.81,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能将其引领
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:46.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿着绿荫大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:54.36,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到达期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看笕那个样子实际上也有迷糊的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该喜欢细心会照顾人的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会喜欢会做饭的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前他说过会做土豆炖肉的女生很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长是很酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该喜欢同类型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  他很会配合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能喜欢会卖傻的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能得出结论啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  笕的女友不是小太刀妹妹么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的确常和小太刀学姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看上去不像是恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只能问笕学长了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀  这次的委托是不能告诉笕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个  你这星期天有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果不介意的话  请和我们约会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:00.03,TXTI,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(133,263)}星  期  日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太吵了  小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学  现在几点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  读书读到早晨  然后睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会迟到  是不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是笕同学的房间么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用下冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  出门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长不迟到的话  现在早在外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有没洗的餐具  放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就好  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怪不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「黑死馆杀人事件」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「脑髓地狱」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「献给虚无的供物」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是传说中的三大奇书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}注：这三本书并称日本三大推理奇书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕  书要放在书架上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看着不舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该放整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓吧  又不是你住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  当然不会住  我在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说怎么一大早就吵吵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来家里表现自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么随便就进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计较什么  常有的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是邻居啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是可以随便出入的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是要去买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮一击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  你有什么喜欢的店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有常去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道好店的话就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常去的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多可爱风格的  真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我穿了这种衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会有人报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我觉得你很适合呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  至少不会有人报警的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就开始樱庭学姐形象改变大作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件很合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  可爱得不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件也适合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚踩四条船的约会  真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是她们买东西的跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看上去很开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的真命天女是哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能随便选  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要脚踩四条船弄成修罗场哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不希望邻居家出命案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  该说「你真可爱  甜心」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11点45分开始吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排得真细
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想好了时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  完美的约会路线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因  因为白崎很期待约会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你调查得好详细
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  最后去的能看到夕阳的小丘公园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向意中人告白的经典场所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没时间了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长的队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为美食节目介绍过好几次这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  排队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  现在排估计要等上一小时的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我应该预约的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  这样正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月我手头紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然难得你找了家好店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去那种店我更安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不会变通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种固执不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕和小玉果然般配
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不刻意地为女性圆场  得分很高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起恋人  更像是搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有人想比试比试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园你玩这种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我每天都有锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  千莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御园同学好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道看哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  方便活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我  有多余的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下好  得分很高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样看起来好像被命令舔脚的变态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开玩笑  看来没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拍过那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就都是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百万伏特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长  再靠近些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你不好意思了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是个男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  朋友说  有的情侣会在这密闭空间接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的好表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉那种让人放不下的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能正合笕学长性格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看上去是御园在以欺负笕为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢噢  我找了好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工厂摄影集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助你兴趣好特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  同好其实有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长  这些都要买吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月不是手头紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以挑了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些书真是种类各异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长难道你是滥读型的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是不挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什么推荐的书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢什么样的书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这样真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次和男生谈书谈得这么投机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣相投果然重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕学长和佳奈在一起时总是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是好搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.33,TXTD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2DDD2&\frx6\fry342\pos(329,256)\frz13.9}悬疑类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的在图书部下赌注的事  怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然记得呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得是重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  是赌赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  习惯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被有特别感情的人看着的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.50,TXTD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&HFFFDFF&}你了解真正的自己吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我记得这里有饮食区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  愉快的约会到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来有牧羊人的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎的命运将要发生巨大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎她？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…任务开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来很有可能以艺术家的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下许多名垂青史的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是即将发生的与白崎的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会极大地改变他的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对白崎一见钟情  当场向她表白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被委婉拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不肯放弃  不停继续着攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…变成跟踪狂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  貌似放弃了对白崎的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他发挥了他所有的艺术细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出了绝赞的充气娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名为：白崎妹妹18号！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎妹妹18号在全世界激起了巨大的热潮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而白崎作为白崎妹妹18号的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名垂青史
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不是什么不好的未来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那娃娃看起来那么棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  充气娃娃是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是什么…难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用来干那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟有多变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你问我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}那个  我想单吃甜点的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  这样下去会相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕  就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学　在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你也很可爱呢　我的甜心  绪美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  笕同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪美  我可以抱得更紧一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男的和白崎的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该朝着好的方向发展了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  笕学长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕  你这是何等的粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面是有原因的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  听我解释
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小太刀的合谋？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  因为你们好像背着笕在做着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们也主动出击试探
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没头没脑地说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  我们哪会在背地里搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  怎么会在背地里对笕同学做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎学姐  你太好懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总算清楚  你是一个不会撒谎的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了  向笕坦白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道我喜欢的类型？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:23.10,TXTJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(262,55,-80,55,21,6486)}标题：关于图书部的笕同学    发信人：希望匿名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:23.10,TXTJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(278,196,-64,196,21,6486)}我喜欢笕同学。能告诉我笕同学喜欢的类型吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们不清楚笕同学喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在想以我们4人为例的话  会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匿名啊  肯定是恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  多人约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一名没被邀请的可怜部员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  cry  boy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪左大人！只有你能理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遭到反感了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人情报的收集板块？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西是什么时候做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢  很久之前就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱庭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会做这种东西  想不起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有什么头绪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笕同学呢  你有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前牧羊人不是给我们过发邮件吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们就想弄清牧羊人的真实身份…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是老了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢笕同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我笕同学喜欢的类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是希望你能幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我想帮你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连咨询邮件都发了  而你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也成为牧羊人的话  会被大家遗忘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说那么晚才注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魔法图书馆时我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都拥有记载自己人生的书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  牧羊人没有属于自己的书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确地说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「书」这一人类的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成为牧羊人的时候将被抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以牧羊人不会给人留下记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再有寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超越人类的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心不下小伙伴们  跟她们愉快地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗地里却以牧羊人的身份奉献他人奉献社会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道还以为能这么美好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不付出任何代价就想得到巨大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上哪有那么简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就算如此你也想当牧羊人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜放弃与白崎她们的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那个游乐场非常有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个星期日如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时间哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去乘坐各种吓人设施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从什么时候开始  变得不想舍弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要放弃牧羊人考试的话请趁早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甘愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为牧羊人  从所有人的记忆中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为牧羊人  引导世界向着好的方向发展
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  我已经做好放弃一切的觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我也会忘了你的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你会忘记我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  你也同样会把我忘得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经舍弃一切了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要强烈质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在图书部毫无地位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身为图书部创始人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近完全沦为龙套了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连休息日都没被邀请参加多人约会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有存在意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  能帮我拿一下架子上的盒子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常乐意
